title: "EDN CONFIRM-1: June 2026 Evaluation Results"
abstract: >-
  Sealed reproduction artefacts for the CONFIRM-1 confirmation campaign
  evaluating EDN, a provenance-governed external memory middleware for
  multi-session LLM assistants, on LongMemEval-S. Fifteen sealed run
  packages across five configurations, three runs each.
